{"id":12,"date":"2025-05-02T18:39:10","date_gmt":"2025-05-02T18:39:10","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/jbx.ail.mybluehost.me\/website_02d9b540\/?page_id=12"},"modified":"2026-02-03T05:53:49","modified_gmt":"2026-02-02T23:53:49","slug":"our-program","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/our-program\/","title":{"rendered":"Our Program"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; use_background_color_gradient=&#8221;on&#8221; background_color_gradient_stops=&#8221;rgba(0,78,133,0.3) 1%|rgba(0,78,133,0.3) 99%&#8221; background_color_gradient_overlays_image=&#8221;on&#8221; background_image=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/a-joyful-family-bonding-moment-2025-09-29-13-16-07-utc.jpg&#8221; min_height=&#8221;687px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||3px|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;282px||||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_text_color=&#8221;#FFFFFF&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">A Partner In Your Journey.<\/span><\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; min_height=&#8221;997.7px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-99c2e60a9f894a99755e\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-99c2e60a9f894a99755e\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\">\n<h2 class=\"preFade fadeIn\">Our Programs<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-cdf9359aa850cf21cbad\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-cdf9359aa850cf21cbad\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;||0px|||&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;]<\/p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">At Kuska Autism Services, we provide high-quality ABA therapy in Utah, serving families in Bountiful, Draper, and surrounding areas. Our programs are rooted in evidence-based Applied Behavior Analysis principles, designed specifically for children with autism spectrum disorder (ASD) or developmental delays. Whether your child needs intensive skill-building or targeted support, we create individualized plans that fit your family&#8217;s lifestyle, schedule, and goals. With flexible delivery options\u2014including in-home ABA therapy in Utah, clinic-based sessions at either our Bountiful or Draper locations, or a hybrid model\u2014we make effective therapy accessible without long waitlists. Morning and daytime hours are available, so families can start seeing meaningful progress sooner.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/11\/mum-and-son-spending-time-together-2025-10-10-00-28-11-utc-scaled.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;mum-and-son-spending-time-together-2025-10-10-00-28-11-utc&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;||0px|||&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/Our-Program-1.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Our Program 1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2 class=\"preFade fadeIn\">Therapy Services Truly Tailored To Your Family<\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<section data-test=\"page-section\" data-section-theme=\"white\" class=\"page-section \n    \n      full-bleed-section\n      layout-engine-section\n    \n    background-width--full-bleed\n    \n      section-height--medium\n    \n    \n      content-width--wide\n    \n    horizontal-alignment--center\n    vertical-alignment--middle\n    \n      \n    \n    \n    white\" data-section-id=\"67460984fce7de7930135caf\" data-controller=\"SectionWrapperController\" data-current-styles=\"{\n&quot;imageOverlayOpacity&quot;: 0.15,\n&quot;backgroundWidth&quot;: &quot;background-width--full-bleed&quot;,\n&quot;sectionHeight&quot;: &quot;section-height--medium&quot;,\n&quot;customSectionHeight&quot;: 10,\n&quot;horizontalAlignment&quot;: &quot;horizontal-alignment--center&quot;,\n&quot;verticalAlignment&quot;: &quot;vertical-alignment--middle&quot;,\n&quot;contentWidth&quot;: &quot;content-width--wide&quot;,\n&quot;customContentWidth&quot;: 50,\n&quot;sectionTheme&quot;: &quot;white&quot;,\n&quot;sectionAnimation&quot;: &quot;none&quot;,\n&quot;backgroundMode&quot;: &quot;image&quot;\n}\" data-current-context=\"{\n&quot;video&quot;: {\n&quot;playbackSpeed&quot;: 0.5,\n&quot;filter&quot;: 1,\n&quot;filterStrength&quot;: 0,\n&quot;zoom&quot;: 0,\n&quot;videoSourceProvider&quot;: &quot;none&quot;\n},\n&quot;backgroundImageId&quot;: null,\n&quot;backgroundMediaEffect&quot;: null,\n&quot;divider&quot;: null,\n&quot;typeName&quot;: &quot;page&quot;\n}\" data-animation=\"none\" data-fluid-engine-section=\"\" data-controllers-bound=\"SectionWrapperController\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746216392665_79\" data-active=\"true\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"content-wrapper\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746216392665_78\">\n<div class=\"content\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746216392665_77\">\n<div data-fluid-engine=\"true\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746216392665_76\">\n<div class=\"fluid-engine fe-67460984fce7de7930135cae\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1746216392665_75\">\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-36cc964f437759b5501c\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-36cc964f437759b5501c\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\">\n<p class=\"sqsrte-large preFade fadeIn\">ABA therapy services that are designed to meet the unique needs of each individual with autism spectrum disorder (ASD). At Kuska, we offer a range of options for service delivery, including in-clinic, in-home, and hybrid schedules.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section data-test=\"page-section\" data-section-theme=\"dark\" class=\"page-section \n    \n      full-bleed-section\n      layout-engine-section\n    \n    background-width--full-bleed\n    \n      section-height--medium\n    \n    \n      content-width--wide\n    \n    horizontal-alignment--center\n    vertical-alignment--middle\n    \n      \n    \n    \n    dark\" data-section-id=\"6751fed1db5343527c42d288\" data-controller=\"SectionWrapperController\" data-current-styles=\"{\n&quot;imageOverlayOpacity&quot;: 0.15,\n&quot;backgroundWidth&quot;: &quot;background-width--full-bleed&quot;,\n&quot;sectionHeight&quot;: &quot;section-height--medium&quot;,\n&quot;customSectionHeight&quot;: 10,\n&quot;horizontalAlignment&quot;: &quot;horizontal-alignment--center&quot;,\n&quot;verticalAlignment&quot;: &quot;vertical-alignment--middle&quot;,\n&quot;contentWidth&quot;: &quot;content-width--wide&quot;,\n&quot;customContentWidth&quot;: 50,\n&quot;backgroundColor&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n&quot;sectionTheme&quot;: &quot;dark&quot;,\n&quot;sectionAnimation&quot;: &quot;none&quot;,\n&quot;backgroundMode&quot;: &quot;image&quot;\n}\" data-current-context=\"{\n&quot;video&quot;: {\n&quot;playbackSpeed&quot;: 0.5,\n&quot;filter&quot;: 1,\n&quot;filterStrength&quot;: 0,\n&quot;zoom&quot;: 0,\n&quot;videoSourceProvider&quot;: &quot;none&quot;\n},\n&quot;backgroundImageId&quot;: null,\n&quot;backgroundMediaEffect&quot;: {\n&quot;type&quot;: &quot;none&quot;\n},\n&quot;divider&quot;: {\n&quot;enabled&quot;: false\n},\n&quot;typeName&quot;: &quot;page&quot;\n}\" data-animation=\"none\" data-fluid-engine-section=\"\" data-controllers-bound=\"SectionWrapperController\" data-active=\"true\"><\/p>\n<div class=\"section-border\"><\/div>\n<\/section>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-yui_3_17_2_1_1733425246892_52927\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-yui_3_17_2_1_1733425246892_52927\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\">\n<h2 class=\"preFade fadeIn\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Our Services<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-05a981ffa639762e3d83\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-05a981ffa639762e3d83\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"preFade fadeIn\">Comprehensive ABA Programs<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-05a981ffa639762e3d83\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-05a981ffa639762e3d83\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\">\n<p dir=\"auto\">Our comprehensive ABA program in Utah follows an intensive model, typically involving 30\u201335 hours of therapy per week. This approach is ideal for children who benefit from broad, consistent support across multiple developmental domains. A Board Certified Behavior Analyst (BCBA) conducts a thorough assessment to identify strengths, challenges, and priority areas. From there, we develop a customized treatment plan with clear, measurable goals. Direct therapy is delivered by trained Registered Behavior Technicians (RBTs) under close BCBA supervision, ensuring high-quality implementation and frequent data review for adjustments. Parents and caregivers receive regular training to generalize skills at home, school, and in the community. Many families in Utah choose this model for younger children or those needing foundational skills in communication, social interaction, and independence\u2014leading to lasting improvements in daily functioning and quality of life.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-55e2e6606ef96a64255a\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-55e2e6606ef96a64255a\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"preFade fadeIn\">Focused ABA Programs<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"fe-block fe-block-55e2e6606ef96a64255a\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html\" data-blend-mode=\"NORMAL\" data-block-type=\"2\" data-border-radii=\"{&quot;topLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;topRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0},&quot;bottomRight&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0}}\" id=\"block-55e2e6606ef96a64255a\">\n<div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\n<div class=\"sqs-html-content\">\n<p dir=\"auto\">For children with more targeted needs, our focused ABA therapy in Utah provides 15\u201325 hours per week, based on clinical recommendations from the initial assessment and your family&#8217;s availability. This model concentrates on specific priorities\u2014such as reducing challenging behaviors, improving a key social skill, or building independence in daily routines\u2014while still delivering evidence-based intervention. Sessions are flexible and can be scheduled around school or other commitments. BCBA oversight ensures progress tracking and parent coaching, so skills transfer beyond therapy hours. This approach works well for older children, those with milder support needs, or families transitioning from more intensive programs.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_button button_text=&#8221;Learn More&#8221; button_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_button][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; specialty=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/page-3.webp&#8221; title_text=&#8221;page-3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|608px|608px|608px|608px&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; specialty_columns=&#8221;2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; custom_padding__hover=&#8221;|||&#8221;][et_pb_row_inner _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column_inner saved_specialty_column_type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<h2>Empowering individuals through personalized treatment<\/h2>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||19px|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span>We believe every child is unique in their own way. This is why we tailor our approach to meet each child\u2019s unique needs and strengths, helping them develop important life skills and achieve better outcomes.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||-12px|||&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;||0px|||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_row_inner et_pb_row_inner_1 et_pb_gutters1\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_column_inner et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_inner et_pb_column_inner_1 et-last-child et_had_animation\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_5  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\">\n<h3>Supporting Individuals in a Variety of Areas Including:<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column_inner][\/et_pb_row_inner][et_pb_row_inner column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;-15px|||||&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column_inner type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; saved_specialty_column_type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; ul_font_size=&#8221;22px&#8221; ul_line_height=&#8221;1.4em&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_blurb et_pb_blurb_1  et_pb_text_align_left  et_pb_blurb_position_left et_pb_bg_layout_light\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_content\">\n<div class=\"et_pb_blurb_container\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"et_pb_module_header\"><span>Social Skills<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Daily Living Skills<\/li>\n<li class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Behavior Management<\/li>\n<li class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Speech &amp; Communication<\/li>\n<li class=\"et_pb_module_header\">Behavior Support Planning<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column_inner][et_pb_column_inner type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; saved_specialty_column_type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; ul_font_size=&#8221;22px&#8221; ul_line_height=&#8221;1.4em&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cognitive Skills<\/li>\n<li>Adaptive Skills<\/li>\n<li>Play &amp; Leisure Skills<\/li>\n<li>Problem Solving &amp; Decision Making<\/li>\n<li>Self Advocacy<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column_inner][\/et_pb_row_inner][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_section]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A Partner In Your Journey. Our Programs At Kuska Autism Services, we provide high-quality ABA therapy in Utah, serving families in Bountiful, Draper, and surrounding areas. Our programs are rooted in evidence-based Applied Behavior Analysis principles, designed specifically for children with autism spectrum disorder (ASD) or developmental delays. Whether your child needs intensive skill-building or [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","_et_pb_use_builder":"on","_et_pb_old_content":"<!-- wp:divi\/placeholder \/-->","_et_gb_content_width":"","footnotes":""},"difl_page_category":[],"class_list":["post-12","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=12"}],"version-history":[{"count":19,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":738,"href":"https:\/\/kuska.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12\/revisions\/738"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/kusk